thread.title: SpaceX's Dragon cargo ship returns to Earth

title: SpaceX's Dragon cargo ship returns to Earth
text:
SpaceX's Dragon cargo ship returns to Earth 3:03pm EST - 01:04 
The SpaceX Dragon cargo spacecraft, carrying supplies and scientific materials, was successfully released from the International Space Station on Saturday and landed in the Pacific Ocean, after a month-long delivery mission for NASA. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
